utpannarūpāddevatāṃ pratipādya mantraṃ pratipādayannāha—jalpanamityādi | ālikālyoḥ prajñopāyarūpayoḥ paramamantratvātsarva eva tadrūpatvājjalpo japa ityeṣa niṣprapañco mantraḥ |

<commentary>karasphoṭo bhavenmudrā aṅgulyāmoṭanaṃ tathetyatra hetumanupanyasyannevaṃ darśayati | aparimitā vyāpārā yoginām | sarvatra hetūpanyāse vistaraḥ syāt | sarva eva tvasau prajñopāyamayatayā maṇḍalamudrārūpo 'vagantavya iti |
nanvevaṃ bhāvyabhāvakabhāvanānupapattāvutpanne ca maṇḍale nirdiṣṭe dhyeyadhyāne kiṃ sarvathotpādite eva | netyāha—taddhyeyamityādi |</commentary>

vikṣepa eva na dhyānamiti dhyeyamapi tanna syādityāha—pitarītyādi | tatsukhaṃ bhujyate svayamiti yathopadeśamajasraṃ yauvanābhiṣekayorvā | evamādimadhyāvasāneṣu yatsukhamanuparatamanubhūyate tatsukhaṃ dhyānamucyate | mahāsukhasyānusmaraṇātkuto vikṣepo yato na dhyānadhyeye | athavā pitarīti gurāvabhiṣekakāle yatprāptamanubhūtaṃ sahajamahāsukhaṃ tadbhujyata ābhujyate svayamanyadāpi |